\par }\pard \s20\ql \fi-547\li1224\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin1224\itap0 {\f28 408.2d Playing a land is a special action consisting of putting that land into play. (See rule 214.9, \'93Lands.\'94)
