\par }\pard\plain \s18\ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0 \f28\fs22\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {
\par 409. Playing Spells and Activated Abilities
\par 
\par }\pard\plain \s17\ql \fi-432\li749\ri0\widctlpar\tx440\tx740\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin749\itap0 \f28\fs22\lang1033\langfe1033\cgrid\langnp1033\langfenp1033 {
409.1. Playing a spell or activated ability follows the steps listed below, in order. If, at any point during the playing of a spell or ability, a
