s controller normally would do so. If the spell or ability instructs both players to do something at the same time as it\rquote s being played, the spell\rquote s controller goes first, then his or her opponent. This applies to all parts of rule 409.1.

\par }\pard \s17\ql \fi-432\li749\ri0\sl-220\slmult0\widctlpar\tx440\tx740\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin749\itap0 {
