\par }\pard \s20\ql \fi-547\li1224\ri0\widctlpar\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin1224\itap0 {\f28 409.1b If the spell or ability is modal (uses the phrase \'93Choose one \emdash \'94 or \'93[specified player] chooses one \emdash \'94
